This product includes software developed for FSOT 2.1–aligned historical
language translation research.

Optional third-party data (not redistributed in this repository unless
explicitly included under their own terms):

  - Pleiades Gazetteer of Ancient Places (https://pleiades.stoa.org)
    CC-BY / project terms — see Pleiades licensing for redistributed dumps.
  - Wiktionary-derived dictionary extracts (local Dictionary.db)
  - Unicode Unikemet Egyptian hieroglyph data (as applicable)

Large training corpora remain on the author's local training drive and are
not part of the Apache-2.0 source distribution unless separately published.
